{"tid":1691213,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"反抗第一步，建立反擊訊號","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T02:51:14.000Z","uid":333360,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d53404dfd2954f4c0baef49aef11846042fec1","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"黑警權力凌駕一切，民權法同區選成功佢地都未必會驚，我地要兩手準備，保護自己同身邊既手足。<br />\n<br />\n反抗第一步建立進攻同反擊既訊號<br />\n<br />\n最近多左post叫打狗救手足，但都係有理無理都恐慌性咁跑，主要係因爲訊息唔流通做成。的的確確唔係每一個手足夠膽打狗，但我亦都相信仲有好多手足會為救手足願意衝前打狗，上星期尖咀第一戰可見一斑。 而呢類手足唔一定係前線，可能係二三線，而往往岀事既時侯恐慌性咁走會帶走埋呢一類既手足，而手足係根本唔知發生緊乜事。 而建立反攻訊號係希望效率咁集結呢班手足，短時間內增加番前線既人數。更重要既係令大家知道一齊上，點解衣大家咁淆底，因為無人帶頭，個個都唔敢帶，所以用一個訊號通知大家一齊救手足，唔好掛住自己走，只要夠多人一定救到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訊號方面我有個建議，拎啲防狼器去，拉着好響v v聲果隻，比啲真前線手足。 當合適既時候前線認為要反擊，就拉響佢。 姐係代替大叫打波有無人跟隊，其實二三線好多夠膽打狗但唔齊裝既手足，咁呢類既人聽到就即番轉頭。共戰黑狗。<br />\n<br />\n呢方法仲有一個好大既作用，行為係會感染其他人，你見人地唔走，你都會定啲唔會走。 <br />\n<br />\n我地急需要一次成功反擊，成功一次自然有人跟，班狗先會驚。班狗唔係神，只要夠人多佢地都會縮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1Ag9uN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1Ag9uN.gif&h=cc0035ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9ce34b7bf0b315c203f6f50bcfdb3e8f90dec62","tid":1691213,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:07:13.000Z","msg":"一齊宣揚反抗意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66f19efc38779e75ecde2bed4693c85e16d32ca","tid":1691213,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"紳士VS殺人魔<br />\n紳士全族死清光"},{"pid":"235828b0ebc3deb683bc02bac59d862f304044cf","tid":1691213,"uid":315626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"要比手足知道有人會跟上"},{"pid":"f4620c6f7e97a9ebee5a5c113632960b18305912","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"235828b0ebc3deb683bc02bac59d862f304044cf","tid":1691213,"uid":315626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"要比手足知道有人會跟上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"無錯，只要一齊上。畜龍都會縮"},{"pid":"1ffdae33f666e665537de3496522965f2a3e0d7a","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66f19efc38779e75ecde2bed4693c85e16d32ca","tid":1691213,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"紳士VS殺人魔<br />\n紳士全族死清光"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"衣家講緊有無不反都照開打，的士佬撞人唔洗比人告，仲唔自救？等乜野？"},{"pid":"b63d58573e290611393ff945e63ec46f0c7c5637","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9ce34b7bf0b315c203f6f50bcfdb3e8f90dec62","tid":1691213,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:07:13.000Z","msg":"一齊宣揚反抗意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"無錯，有意識大家一齊上。 只要成功開到一次先例就會好多人跟。"},{"pid":"117742ddc73b1fa0c8f39cb121e1da3a0fd255cd","tid":1691213,"uid":143399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"信號係必要  同要傾定目標係做到邊一不<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1661816d9611f384262285eca4ae8b6557d1db60","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117742ddc73b1fa0c8f39cb121e1da3a0fd255cd","tid":1691213,"uid":143399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"信號係必要  同要傾定目標係做到邊一不<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"個訊號我認為唔可以係口叫，因為現實好嘈同可能有人叫口號，根本聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發號施令既最好係最前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為佢地最清楚前面咩環境，亦都可以傷為求救訊號，通知後方要番轉頭救手足。我提議用防狼器係因爲暫時未有人用，夠獨特又夠響。咁一聽到就知乜事，如果認同既麻煩各位幫忙廣傳一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地衣家真係好需要成功反擊"},{"pid":"a8a4681e2c14e67c5d8bc3f95f5f1b897b7a3b38","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117742ddc73b1fa0c8f39cb121e1da3a0fd255cd","tid":1691213,"uid":143399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"信號係必要  同要傾定目標係做到邊一不<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"首要目標，係起碼守得到佢衝過無人被捕，真心，衣家話不受傷不流血真係無乜可能，對家用咩武力我地控制唔到，但希望堅守到不被捕"},{"pid":"c8fce8e4b1fe9c76d08895d8b90d36d848aa7940","tid":1691213,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人<br />\n還拖</span></span>"},{"pid":"417c622bf6dd4e2544813af408a79f20bd884ad2","tid":1691213,"uid":10809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd46388dcc48354afb00336a168f51cd500a4cb7","tid":1691213,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"反抗第一步係要最前線 有反擊意向先<br />\n得訊號 有衝前反擊必死決心 咩都死"},{"pid":"5cb523db55bb65f9b19f562effe84c3d7af1881f","tid":1691213,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"13a4839d789696046363699bce8f689c95c61164","tid":1691213,"uid":205176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"有無人跟隊！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"72c17d7921c29b2efd38ce4e661380fe1d80d013","tid":1691213,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd46388dcc48354afb00336a168f51cd500a4cb7","tid":1691213,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite